<div class="section" id="return-values">
<h2><a class="toc-backref" href="#id6">Return Values</a><a class="headerlink" href="#return-values" title="Permalink to this headline">Â¶</a></h2>
<p>Common return values are documented <a class="reference internal" href="../../../reference_appendices/common_return_values.html#common-return-values"><span class="std std-ref">here</span></a>, the following are the fields unique to this module:</p>
<table border=0 cellpadding=0 class="documentation-table">
    <tr>
        <th colspan="1">Key</th>
        <th>Returned</th>
        <th width="100%">Description</th>
    </tr>
                <tr>
                            <td colspan="1">
                <div class="ansibleOptionAnchor" id="return-elapsed"></div>
                <b>elapsed</b>
                <a class="ansibleOptionLink" href="#return-elapsed" title="Permalink to this return value"></a>
                <div style="font-size: small">
                  <span style="color: purple">integer</span>
                                      </div>
                                </td>
            <td>always</td>
            <td>
                                        <div>The number of seconds that elapsed while waiting</div>
                                    <br/>
                                        <div style="font-size: smaller"><b>Sample:</b></div>
                                            <div style="font-size: smaller; color: blue; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;">23</div>
                                </td>
        </tr>
                            <tr>
                            <td colspan="1">
                <div class="ansibleOptionAnchor" id="return-match_groupdict"></div>
                <b>match_groupdict</b>
                <a class="ansibleOptionLink" href="#return-match_groupdict" title="Permalink to this return value"></a>
                <div style="font-size: small">
                  <span style="color: purple">dictionary</span>
                                      </div>
                                </td>
            <td>always</td>
            <td>
                                        <div>Dictionary containing all the named subgroups of the match, keyed by the subgroup name, as returned by <a href='https://docs.python.org/2/library/re.html#re.MatchObject.groupdict'>https://docs.python.org/2/library/re.html#re.MatchObject.groupdict</a></div>
                                    <br/>
                                        <div style="font-size: smaller"><b>Sample:</b></div>
                                            <div style="font-size: smaller; color: blue; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;">{&#x27;group&#x27;: &#x27;match&#x27;}</div>
                                </td>
        </tr>
                            <tr>
                            <td colspan="1">
                <div class="ansibleOptionAnchor" id="return-match_groups"></div>
                <b>match_groups</b>
                <a class="ansibleOptionLink" href="#return-match_groups" title="Permalink to this return value"></a>
                <div style="font-size: small">
                  <span style="color: purple">list</span>
                   / <span style="color: purple">elements=string</span>                    </div>
                                </td>
            <td>always</td>
            <td>
                                        <div>Tuple containing all the subgroups of the match as returned by <a href='https://docs.python.org/2/library/re.html#re.MatchObject.groups'>https://docs.python.org/2/library/re.html#re.MatchObject.groups</a></div>
                                    <br/>
                                        <div style="font-size: smaller"><b>Sample:</b></div>
                                            <div style="font-size: smaller; color: blue; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;">[&#x27;match 1&#x27;, &#x27;match 2&#x27;]</div>
                                </td>
        </tr>
                    </table>
